    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that feels so hollow. \"making a difference\" feels like a lie when you see the data. it's not just bad news, it's like the actual foundation of life is collapsing. how can anyone be expected to just \"carry on\" and act like everything is fine when the future is objectively terrifying? it's hard not to feel like there's literally no point to any of it anymore.",
